Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正喵鸣\c&H282828&\bord0\fs35\\frz2.097\pos(859.2,111.4)}好久没听到JK的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正喵鸣\c&H4A4A4A&\bord0\fs35\frz13.78\pos(1120,300.2)}只是看一眼
